These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Sport: skateboarding, basketball, biathlon, cricket
Game: monopoly, domino, poker, chess
1. Game:chess is on the left of Sport:biathlon##1
2. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Game:domino##1
3. Sport:cricket is in an odd position##4
4. Game:poker is on the left or right of Game:chess##3
5. Sport:skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball | cricket | biathlon |
| Game        | monopoly | domino   | chess | poker    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
City: berlin, venice, marseilles, colone
Cigar: fonseca, game, cain, siglo
1. City:venice is on the left of City:colone##1
2. Cigar:fonseca is on the left of Cigar:cain##1
3. Cigar:cain is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:fonseca == City:berlin##1
5. Cigar:game is on the right of Cigar:cain##1
6. Cigar:fonseca == City:berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| City   | marseilles | berlin  | venice  | colone |
| Cigar   | siglo    | fonseca | cain | game    |

