.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: funk, country, metal, salsa
Game: whist, backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg
1. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left or right of Game:mah-jongg##3
2. Music-Genre:metal is in an even position##4
3. Game:mah-jongg is on the left or right of Music-Genre:country##3
4. Game:mah-jongg is on the right of Game:snooker##1
5. Game:whist is in an odd position##4
6. Music-Genre:country is on the right of Music-Genre:metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre          | salsa | metal | country    | funk      |
| Game   | snooker        | mah-jongg     | whist | backgammon |

