2. Beverage:coffee is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
3. Nationality:russian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:malaysian is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Nationality:malaysian is on the right of Beverage:mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage         | coffee | mirinda | iced-tea | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | russian       | polish   | malaysian    | turkish  |

