2. Flower:balloon-flower == Cigar:prince##1
3. Flower:sunflower is on the right of Cigar:aristoff##1
4. Cigar:dannemann is on the far left##1
5. Cigar:blend is in an odd position##4
6. Flower:zinnia is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | aristoff    | blend   | prince       |
| Flower   | zinnia | bellflower | sunflower | balloon-flower |

