2. Flower:begonia is in an odd position##4
3. Food:grapes is on the left or right of Flower:begonia##3
4. Flower:begonia is on the right of Food:grapes##1
5. Flower:azalea is between Flower:begonia and Flower:bellflower##2
6. Food:radish is in an odd position##4
7. Food:radish is between Flower:azalea and Food:blueberry##2
