2. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Flower:bellflower##1
3. Hobby:chess is between Hobby:hiking and Flower:dahlia##2
4. Flower:bellflower is in an odd position##4
5. Hobby:chess is on the left or right of Hobby:hiking##3
6. Flower:iris is on the left or right of Hobby:skydiving##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Flower      | iris       | dahlia   | bellflower | balloon-flower |
| Hobby   | traveling | skydiving | chess        | hiking    |

