2. Color:white is on the left or right of Color:pink##3
3. Color:green is on the far left or far right##3
4. Movie-Genre:sports is on the left of Movie-Genre:western##1
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Color:pink##1
6. Movie-Genre:sports is in an even position##4
7. Movie-Genre:time-travel == Color:red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Color   | green | pink    | white       | red |
| Movie-Genre       | satire  | sports | western | time-travel  |

